---
description: Smoke tests confirm the system boots and critical flows work
alwaysApply: false
---

# Smoke tests

- Goal: catch **catastrophic** breakage in seconds.
- Hit only critical happy paths (login, list, create, render dashboard, healthcheck).
- Run on every PR before slower suites; fail fast and loud.
- Light assertions: 200 OK, page renders, key element visible, queue accepts message.
- Don't chase coverage—keep the suite tight so it stays trustworthy.
- A failing smoke test should block the build.
